S.FORM: = Philippe of Belgium = Mntucing hngkawas 1960 idas 4 jiyax 15 ka Philippe of Belgium ga, empklaw ka hiya. Bukung klwaan Belguim ta sayang o kiya ka Philippe of Belgium, pnaah hngkawas 2313 idas 7 jiyax 21 pnrajing kmlawa klwaan. = Philip Bukung Belgium = Philip (phnang kari Netherlands: (fi.lɪp), kngkawas 1960 idas 4 diyax 15) ka Sediq Belgium Na Bukong Qnlhangan. Philip pa kiya ka laqi snaw qbsuran Albert II Bukung Qnlhangan mi Paola Qridin Bukung. Kngkawas 2013 idas 7 diyax 21 cida, tama niya alaw mnarux ka qbubur dmi malax qpahun niya mBukung daw, Philip ka rmirih qpahun mBukung. Philip pa mniq kngkawas 1999 cida tuhuy Mathilde d'Udekem d'Acoz msturung, kiya mi msupu tnquli 4 laqi. Kndusan cuxal Philip pa mntuting kngkawas 1960 idas 4 diyax 15. Albert Cinwang ka tama niya, bubu niya ka Reyj Kongcu Paola. Mntuting 1 idas daw, Philip u mniq Brussels (sotu na Belgium) na Pnrhulan Saint Jacques-sur-Coudenberg psdhu ptwaya pcuyuq qsiya, kiya mi dmuwi hangan tama rudan tama rudan niya Vloandern Philip Cinwang muda tmhangan Philip. Kyoiku Kngkawas 1978 dhuq kngkawas 1981 cida, Philip u mniq tu118 kay "Promotion Toutes Armes" cida muyas Belgium Pyasan Hwangcya Cyuns Sweyweyn. Kngkawas 1980 idas 9 diyax 26 cida, Philip u wada phyuwan Sawwey mi wada psdhuwan phiyu. Philip u lmutuc mniq Turu Kingal Sweyweyn, Pyasan Tubeyhing Oxford muyas, Philip u tumal keyngkyosey ying mniq Pyasan Tubeyhing Sttanford muyas, kiya u mniq kngkawas 1985 mnhdu muyas, wada mangal Seyjiswey Swos Sweywey. Kiya uri u Philip pa wada mangal Mcbu Skoki Palic Mpskaya Niya, kiya mi patas meyngkyo Rakasang mi Tuci Tuyweyn uri. Mnsturung Philip pa mniq kngkawas 1999 idas 12 diyax 4 cida tuhuy Mathilde d'Udekem d'Acoz msturung, kiya mi niqan 4 laqi dha: Elizabeth Kongcu, Gabriel Wangc, Ringkwang Wangc mi Eleonore Kongcu. Bukung Qnlhangan Philip mi Qridin Bukung Mathilde msdungus muda pkla kari mnhdu psdhuwan burah Bukung Belgium daw, mpniq Brusselssnquri ssediq muda phiyu bawa smqaras. Snquri qnlhangan icil mawyi Kngkawas 1993 idas 8 diyax 6 cida, seyhu Belgium u muda phiyu Philip ngalan Belgium Mquri Nganguc Mawyi Weyweynhuy (BFTB) Minggi Cusi. Philip ka rmirih tama niya snpeyyah kngkawas 1962 prading ngalan BFTB Minggi Cusi. Kngkawas 2003 idas 5 diyax 3 cida, Philip u wada phyuwan Waymawsu Minggi Cusi, rmirih BFTB. Tumal Bukung Qnlhangan Albert II pa mniq kngkawas 2013 idas 7 diyax 21 malax qpahan Bukung, Philip Cinwang ka psdhuwan phiyu Bukung Qnlhangan Belgium. Qbsuran laqi qridin Philip Elizabeth Kongcu ka mpririh hiya hiti, mpmusa mwaya tu1 Bukung Qridin Qnlhangan Belgium. Qmlahang Philip pa mniq mnhdu kngkawas 2014 Belgium Ryeynpang Knbeyhing Seyngkyo daw, mniq quri so msupu phiyu pnspuwan seyhu pa niqan balay dndulan niya. Kngkawas 2019 idas 5 cida, Philip u mtqita dqras Vlaams Belang Congcay Tom Van Grieken, niyi ka Tang dha mntxal balay muda syotay Hwangs kwancong. Kngkawas 2020 cida, Philip u muda pkla kari pquri so ndan dha cbiyaw mniq mnBelgium na Congo "Mqnaqah Nuda Pphuqil mi Tmseyyax" u muda psruwa qnquwan dha mi qnnaqah kuxul niya. Knrdax mi ppuniq Knrdax Qnlhangan Knrdax Qnlhangan Icil Ppuniq Papak

= Philippe of Belgiom = Mntocing hngkawas 1960 idas 4 jiyax 15 ka Philippe of Belgiom ga, empklaw ka hiya. Bokong klwaan Belgoim ta sayang o kiya ka Philippe of Belgiom, pnaah hngkawas 2313 idas 7 jiyax 21 pnrajing kmlawa klwaan. = Philip Bokong Belgiom = Philip (phnang kari Netherlands: (fi.lɪp), kngkawas 1960 idas 4 diyax 15) ka Sediq Belgiom Na Bokong Qnlhangan. Philip pa kiya ka laqi snaw qbsoran Albert II Bokong Qnlhangan mi Paola Qridin Bokong. Kngkawas 2013 idas 7 diyax 21 cida, tama niya alaw mnarox ka qbobor dmi malax qpahon niya mBokong daw, Philip ka rmirih qpahon mBokong. Philip pa mniq kngkawas 1999 cida tohoy Mathilde d'Udekem d'Acoz mstorong, kiya mi msopo tnqoli 4 laqi. Kndosan coxal Philip pa mntoting kngkawas 1960 idas 4 diyax 15. Albert Cinwang ka tama niya, bobo niya ka Reyj Kongco Paola. Mntoting 1 idas daw, Philip o mniq Brossels (soto na Belgiom) na Pnrholan Saint Jacqoes-sor-Coodenberg psdho ptwaya pcoyoq qsiya, kiya mi dmowi hangan tama rodan tama rodan niya Vloandern Philip Cinwang moda tmhangan Philip. Kyoiko Kngkawas 1978 dhoq kngkawas 1981 cida, Philip o mniq to118 kay "Promotion Tootes Armes" cida moyas Belgiom Pyasan Hwangcya Cyons Sweyweyn. Kngkawas 1980 idas 9 diyax 26 cida, Philip o wada phyowan Sawwey mi wada psdhowan phiyo. Philip o lmotoc mniq Toro Kingal Sweyweyn, Pyasan Tobeyhing Oxford moyas, Philip o tomal keyngkyosey ying mniq Pyasan Tobeyhing Sttanford moyas, kiya o mniq kngkawas 1985 mnhdo moyas, wada mangal Seyjiswey Swos Sweywey. Kiya ori o Philip pa wada mangal Mcbo Skoki Palic Mpskaya Niya, kiya mi patas meyngkyo Rakasang mi Toci Toyweyn ori. Mnstorong Philip pa mniq kngkawas 1999 idas 12 diyax 4 cida tohoy Mathilde d'Udekem d'Acoz mstorong, kiya mi niqan 4 laqi dha: Elizabeth Kongco, Gabriel Wangc, Ringkwang Wangc mi Eleonore Kongco. Bokong Qnlhangan Philip mi Qridin Bokong Mathilde msdongos moda pkla kari mnhdo psdhowan borah Bokong Belgiom daw, mpniq Brosselssnqori ssediq moda phiyo bawa smqaras. Snqori qnlhangan icil mawyi Kngkawas 1993 idas 8 diyax 6 cida, seyho Belgiom o moda phiyo Philip ngalan Belgiom Mqori Ngangoc Mawyi Weyweynhoy (BFTB) Minggi Cosi. Philip ka rmirih tama niya snpeyyah kngkawas 1962 prading ngalan BFTB Minggi Cosi. Kngkawas 2003 idas 5 diyax 3 cida, Philip o wada phyowan Waymawso Minggi Cosi, rmirih BFTB. Tomal Bokong Qnlhangan Albert II pa mniq kngkawas 2013 idas 7 diyax 21 malax qpahan Bokong, Philip Cinwang ka psdhowan phiyo Bokong Qnlhangan Belgiom. Qbsoran laqi qridin Philip Elizabeth Kongco ka mpririh hiya hiti, mpmosa mwaya to1 Bokong Qridin Qnlhangan Belgiom. Qmlahang Philip pa mniq mnhdo kngkawas 2014 Belgiom Ryeynpang Knbeyhing Seyngkyo daw, mniq qori so msopo phiyo pnspowan seyho pa niqan balay dndolan niya. Kngkawas 2019 idas 5 cida, Philip o mtqita dqras Vlaams Belang Congcay Tom Van Grieken, niyi ka Tang dha mntxal balay moda syotay Hwangs kwancong. Kngkawas 2020 cida, Philip o moda pkla kari pqori so ndan dha cbiyaw mniq mnBelgiom na Congo "Mqnaqah Noda Pphoqil mi Tmseyyax" o moda psrowa qnqowan dha mi qnnaqah koxol niya.
